ull, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013178, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, this holy place is verily Yours, this situation is Yours, and I am entering here so as to confide to You things that You are more knowledgeable than I am as well as You are more knowledgeable than I am as regards my secrets and my confidential speech. All praise be to Allah, the All-benevolent, the All-favorer, the All-munificent, Who, out of His munificence, has made it easy for me to visit my master, Who has not made me banned from visiting him, and Who has not included me with those who are prevented from being loyal to his (Divinely commissioned) leadership; rather, He has bestowed upon me and donated me (this favor). O Allah, just as You have conferred upon me with the favor of recognition of him, so also (please do) include me with his adherents (Shia) and allow me to enter Paradise by means of his intercession, O most merciful of all those who show mercy.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Be-shak yeh baargah Teri baargah hai, yeh maqaam Tera maqaam hai aur mai us mein daakhil huwa hu, mai Tujh se munajaat kar raha hu keh Tu mujh se ziyadah mere baatin ko jaanta hai. Hamd Khuda ke liye hai jo mohabbat waala, ehsaan waala, ataa waala hai, woh jis ki ataa yeh hai keh apne ehsaan se mere Maula ki ziyarat mujh par aasaan kar di, Us ne mujhe unki ziyarat se baaz (alag) nahi rakkha aur na unki wilaayat se dur kiya hai, bal keh mujh par ataa o bakhshish ki hai. Ay Ma’bood! Jaise Tu ne mujh par Maula ki maarefat ka ehsaan farmaaya hai, pas mujhe un ke shiyyo’n mein qaraar de aur unki shafa’at se mujhe Jannat mein daakhil farma, ay sab se ziyadah rahem waale.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! بے شک یہ بارگاہ تیری بارگاہ ہے یہ مقام تیرا مقام ہے اور میں اس میں داخل ہوا ہوں میں تجھ سے مناجات کررہا ہوں کہ تو مجھ سے زیادہ میرے باطن و راز کوجانتا ہے حمد خدا کے لئے ہے جو محبت والا احسان والا عطا والا ہے وہ جس کی عطا یہ ہے کہ اپنے احسان سے میرے مولا کی زیارت مجھ پر آسان کر دی اس نے مجھے ان کی زیارت سے باز نہیں رکھا اور نہ ان کی ولایت سے دور کیا ہے بلکہ مجھ پر عطا و بخشش کی ہے اے معبود! جیسے تو نے مجھ پر مولا کی معرفت کا احسان فرمایا ہے پس مجھے ان کے شیعوں میں قرار دے اور ان کی شفاعت سے مجھے جنت میں داخل فرما اے سب سے زیادہ رحم کرنے والے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNA HAA-ZAL HARAMA HARAMO-KA WAL MAQAAMA MAQAAMO-KA WA ANAA AD-KHOLO ILAI-HE ONAAJEE-KA BE-MAAA ANTA A’LAMO BEHI MINNEE WA MIN SIRREE WA NAJWAA-YA. ALHAMDO LILLAA-HIL HANNAA-NIL MANNAA-NIL MOTA-TAWWELIL LAZEE MIN TA-TAWWOLE-HI SAHHALA LEE ZIYAA-RATA MAWLAAYA BE EHSAANE-HI WA LAM YAZ-AL’NEE ’AN ZIYAA-RATE-HI MAMNOO’AN WA LAA ’AN WELAAYATE-HI MADFOO’AN BAL TATAW-WALA WA MANAHA. ALLAAHUMMA KA-MAA MA-NANTA A’LAIYYA BE-MA’REFATE-HI FAJ-AL’NEE MIN SHEE-A’TE-HI WA AD-KHILNIL JANNATA BE-SHAFAA-A’TE-HI YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّ هٰذَا الْحَرَمَ حَرَمُكَ وَالْمَقَامَ مَقَامُكَ وَاَنَا اَدْخُلُ اِلَیْهِ اُنَاجِیْكَ بِمَآ اَنْتَ اَعْلَمُ بِهٖ مِنِّیْ وَمِنْ سِرِّیْ وَنَجْوَایَ۔ اَلْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الْحَنَّانِ الْمَنَّانِ الْمُتَطَوِّلِ الَّذِیْ مِنْ تَطَوُّلِهٖ سَهَّلَ لِیْ زِیَارَۃَ مَوْلَایَ بِاِحْسَانِهٖ وَلَمْ یَجْعَلْنِیْ عَنْ زِیَارَتِهٖ مَمْنُوْعًا وَلَا عَنْ وِلَایَتِهٖ مَدْفُوْعًۢا بَلْ تَطَوَّلَ وَمَنَحَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ كَمَا مَنَنْتَ عَلَیَّ بِمَعْرِفَتِهٖ فَاجْعَلْنِیْ مِنْ شِیْعَتِهٖ وَاَدْخِلْنِیْ الْجَنَّۃَ بِشَفَاعَتِهٖ یَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "Arabi